	(text "Manually set ROSC; by default, fsw = 120 kHz\nWith 200k resistor, fsw ≈ 525 kHz (Inverse)\n\nCss (nF) = (tss (ms) * Iss (uA) / Vref (V)\nIss = 2uA, Vref = 0.8V from datasheet\n\nTarget start time of 5ms\nCss = 5 * 2.5 = 12.5 nf ≈ 10 nF (std value)\n\nSchottky Catch Diode\nMust be > Vin; V > 13V, Handle 2A output current\n\nInductor \n\nL = ((Vout)*(Vin - Vout)) / ((Vin)(fsw)(ΔIl)\n- Target ΔIl = 0.6A\n\nL = ((5V)*(12-5)) / ((12)(513000)(0.6))\nL ≈ 10 uH\n\nIsat > 2 A plus headroom\n2 x 2.5 = Isat\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 133.096 129.032 0)
		(effects
			(font
				(size 1.27 1.27)
				(color 0 0 0 1)
			)
			(justify left)
		)
		(uuid "f4bee202-4d4c-4fc8-a2eb-6ad0fe56c1a3")
	)
	(text "Actuator Inputs\n"
		(exclude_from_sim no)
		(at 417.83 96.52 0)
		(effects
